text: East Garden City was a census-designated place (CDP) in the northeast part of the Town of Hempstead, in the central part of Nassau County, New York, United State. It is near the Hempstead/North Hempstead town line. The population was 6,208 at the 2010 census. It is now part of Uniondale CDP. ==References== Category:Census-designated places in New York (state)
title: East Garden City, New York
